## 📈 Slide 13: Optimasi Performa

| Optimasi | Detail |
|----------|--------|
| **Server-side Pagination** | Employee list 20/page, report data 10/page |
| **Parallel API Calls** | Dashboard: Promise.all() untuk 3 API sekaligus |
| **Lazy Loading Images** | `loading="lazy"` pada foto karyawan |
| **Debounced Search** | 400ms delay sebelum trigger API call |
| **CSS-only Animations** | Hanya transform/opacity (GPU accelerated) |
| **Connection Pooling** | PostgreSQL max 10 connections |

